{"id":5100,"title":"Multiple casualties in the Bastion UK Role 3 hospital: personal reflections on the positive evolution of deployed military hospital care.","abstract":"In this article a snapshot of casualty presentations to the UK Role 3 hospital in Camp Bastion, Afghanistan, will be briefly described. The observations allow reflection on the advances and strength of clinical provision at the time of the incident, written from a medical command perspective.","date":"2014-10-22","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25335319","annotations":[{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.492122,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Military","weight":0.371952,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military"},{"name":"United Kingdom","weight":0.353658,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Kingdom"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.309465,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Evolution","weight":0.269179,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evolution"},{"name":"Afghanistan","weight":0.205556,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afghanistan"},{"name":"Casualty (person)","weight":0.19543,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Casualty_(person)"},{"name":"Camp Bastion","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Camp_Bastion"},{"name":"Perspective (graphical)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perspective_(graphical)"},{"name":"Military hospital","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_hospital"},{"name":"Bastion","weight":0.0158689,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bastion"},{"name":"Clinical psychology","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_psychology"},{"name":"Reflection (physics)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Re